<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1899-09-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1899-09-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="775" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d775">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Russell</persName> to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Caracas</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-09-15"><hi rend="italic">September 15,
                                    1899</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Revolutionists took Valencia yesterday. President returning to Caracas.
                            Where is war vessel? Permission granted to make survey mentioned
                            yesterday’s cable.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Russell.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>